<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title> Real Madrid | About Page </title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/styles/imgs/header/real-madrid-logo.png" sizes="64x64">



    <!-- Libraries -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/css/about.css">
</head>

<body>

    <div class="about">
        <section id="imgheader">
            <img id="headerimg" src="/styles/imgs/about/realMadridHeader2.jpeg" alt="headerimg">
        </section>
        <h1 class="title">Who Are We?</h1>

        <section id="whoarewe">
            <p1>
                "An institution that transcends sports, a symbol of passion, excellence, and tradition" <br>
                <span class="font">Our story begins over a century ago when a group of football enthusiasts came
                    together to form what would become one of the most iconic clubs in the world.</span> <br> <br>
            </p1>
            <p2>Founded in 1902, Real Madrid has evolved into one of the most iconic football institutions
                worldwide.<br> From its early struggles to its golden era of the late 1950s and 1960s, marked by
                unprecedented European Cup triumphs, to the modern era of 'Galácticos' dominance, the club has
                consistently set high standards. With a roster of legendary players like Alfredo Di Stéfano, Ferenc
                Puskás, and Cristiano Ronaldo, Real Madrid's legacy is unmatched.<br> La Fabrica, its renowned youth
                academy, continues to produce top talents, while the Santiago Bernabéu Stadium stands as a symbol of the
                club's grandeur.<br> Today, with a star-studded squad, ongoing stadium renovations, and a global
                fanbase, Real Madrid remains at the pinnacle of football excellence.<br>Stay connected with us for the
                latest news, updates, and insights into the club's continued journey towards greatness."
            </p2>
        </section>

        <section id="pictures">
            <div id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel" data-bs-interval="3500">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <img src="/styles/imgs/about/soccer women.webp" class="d-block w-100" alt=".">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="/styles/imgs/about/soccerrrr.jpeg" class="d-block w-100" alt=".">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="/styles/imgs/about/soccer2.jpeg" class="d-block w-100" alt=".">
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <img src="/styles/imgs/about/soccerwinninf.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt=".">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>


        <section id="innumbers">
            <h1>A little in numbers..</h1>
            <p id="titlesCard"><span>La Liga titles</span><span>UEFA Champions League titles</span><span>Copa del Rey
                    titles</span><span>FIFA club world cup</span><span>UEFA Super cup</span></p>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-inner">
                        <div class="card-front">
                            <img src="/styles/imgs/about/award.png" alt="Placeholder Image">
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-back">
                            <div class="side">
                                <p>34</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-inner">
                        <div class="card-front">
                            <img src="/styles/imgs/about/award.png" alt="Placeholder Image">
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-back">
                            <div class="side">
                                <p>13</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-inner">
                        <div class="card-front">
                            <img src="/styles/imgs/about/award.png" alt="Placeholder Image">
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-back">
                            <div class="side">
                                <p>19</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-inner">
                        <div class="card-front">
                            <img src="/styles/imgs/about/award.png" alt="Placeholder Image">
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-back">
                            <div class="side">
                                <p>4</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-inner">
                        <div class="card-front">
                            <img src="/styles/imgs/about/award.png" alt="Placeholder Image">
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-back">
                            <div class="side">
                                <p>3</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="gallery">
            <div class="window">
                <div class="window-content">
                    <img id="soccericon" src="/styles/imgs/about/soccer-ball-variant-removebg-preview.png" alt="">
                    <p class="caption">Football is our heartbeat, our essence. With a history steeped in glory, we have
                        conquered the football world time and time again. From the streets of Madrid to the grand stages
                        of Europe, we have left an indelible mark on this beautiful game.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="window">
                <div class="window-content">
                    <img id="basketballicon" src="/styles/imgs/about/basketball-ball-variant-removebg-preview.png"
                        alt="">
                    <p class="caption">our legacy extends beyond the football pitch. Our basketball team stands tall
                        among the giants of European basketball. With a roster of champions and a hunger for victory, we
                        have dominated the courts, claiming Liga ACB titles and EuroLeague crowns with flair and
                        finesse.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="map">
            <h3>Our stores</h3>
            <!--The div element for the map -->
            <gmp-map center="<%= coords.center.lat %>,<%= coords.center.long %>" zoom="5" map-id="branchesMap" >
                    <!-- Go over all the coords and add markers for them on map -->
                    <% for(let i=0; i< coords.data.length; i++) { %>                      
                        <gmp-advanced-marker position="<%= coords.data[i].lat %>,<%= coords.data[i].long %>" title="<%= coords.data[i].address %>"></gmp-advanced-marker>                  
                        <% } %>
            </gmp-map>
        </section>

    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/5.1.3/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.7.1.min.js"
        integrity="sha256-/JqT3SQfawRcv/BIHPThkBvs0OEvtFFmqPF/lYI/Cxo=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="/js/about.js"></script>
    <!--The JS library for the google map -->
    <script
        src="<%='https://maps.googleapis.com/maps/api/js?key=' + GOOGLE_KEY +'&loading=async&libraries=maps,marker&v=beta'%>"
        defer>
        </script>


</body>

</html>